BricksVFS API Documentation (v0.1.4)

Base URL: http://localhost:8080 (Default)

Read Operations (Public)

ğŸ“‚ List Files

GET /api/files

Query: path (e.g., /Photos)

Response: JSON array of files.

ğŸ” Search

GET /api/search

Query: q (Search term)

Response: JSON array of matching files with full paths.

ğŸ“¥ Download File

GET /api/file

Query: name (Full path to file)

Response: Raw file content with correct MIME type.

ğŸ‘ï¸ Preview Image

GET /api/preview

Query: name (Full path)

Response: Optimized JPEG image (max 1920px).

ğŸ“Š Disk Stats

GET /api/stats

Response: JSON object (total_bytes, used_bytes, free_bytes).

Write Operations (Secured)

Requires Authorization: Basic ... header if root_password is set in config.

